      "type" : "richtext",
      "display_width" : null,
      "default" : "<p>Managing a project-led workforce with varied skills, compliance requirements, and shifting schedules created increasing complexity for the organisation. Elliott Group needed a modern HRMS that could support large-scale projects, subcontractor management, and multi-site operations while improving compliance and reducing administrative burden.</p><p>Elliott Group has been delivering major construction projects since the 1920s. With a reputation built over generations, the company now operates across London, Birmingham, Dublin, and Cork, supported by a skilled workforce of over 275 employees and a large network of subcontractors.</p><p>Their teams have contributed to landmark developments including London 2012, Croke Park, the Irish Times Building, and major healthcare and public sector schemes. Today, Elliott Group continues to work with leading clients such as Google, Dunnes Stores, HSE, Vhi, Whitbread, and Richmond Homes.</p>"
